[{"Code":"en","Title":"Authorized representative requirements","Slug":"authorized-representative-requirements","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvx-uj3eyy-006\">To verify your business, we require information about the <strong>Authorized Representative </strong>who is completing this onboarding process on behalf of your legal entity. </p><p data-block-id=\"mh4dygkf-2ncdex-145\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4dyh4o-bxr4wb-147\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;\">Who is the Authorized Representative?</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4dyh4o-v7gjoe-149\">The <strong>Authorized Representative is the individual who is currently filling out the Xendit onboarding application on behalf of your company</strong>. This person will be our primary point of contact for the application process and must be legally empowered to sign documents and make commitments for the business.</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4e66fd-nhpbzk-026\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvx-87mkyo-007\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"><img data-block-id=\"mh4e2x1h-obfc66-024\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image-1761282186132.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"812\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"yes\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:812px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvy-fcqal0-012\">Required information</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvy-6gom1k-014\">The Authorized Representative must complete the following fields in the onboarding flow:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"727\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:727px;width:727px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:211px;\"><col style=\"width:516px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"211\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e7clw-37iie0-028\">Category</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"516\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e7i6o-9lj40a-031\">Required Details</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"211\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e7rza-m08tf2-053\">Personal Details</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"516\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eboky-xeus5u-131\">First Name, Last Name, Gender, Date of Birth</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"211\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e8w3z-0xxam1-122\">Contact Information</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"516\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4ec21d-ui47kg-134\">Email Address, Phone Number</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"211\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e94tu-h4ruod-124\">Residential Address</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"516\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4echnz-6j8cmf-136\">Full Residential Address (Country, Address Line 1, City, State/Province, Postal Code)</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"211\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e9bal-8r6s7k-126\">Nationality</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"516\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eefs2-64bc1z-141\">Country of Citizenship/Nationality</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"211\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e9g7x-e720rc-128\">Role</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"516\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4efctl-hwmyq7-143\">The representative's official role within the company.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><hr class=\"hr-divider1\" style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(128, 128, 128);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(128, 128, 128) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;line-height:1.15 !important;\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw3-hmnuio-016\">Required verification documents</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw3-vc88co-018\">To confirm the identity and authority of the representative, the following documents must be submitted:</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4dlvlv-5aj77e-010\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"></p><ol data-block-id=\"mh4dmldp-coropw-012\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4dmldp-vrr880-013\"><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4dlvvy-gj8egg-011\">Proof of Identity</h4><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-1e6pxg-022\">You must upload a clear copy of a valid government-issued ID. You will be prompted to select the type of ID you are submitting:</p></li></ol><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-j9kw2l-023\" data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-bibosk-024\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-mz9hqc-025\">National ID (e.g., KTP, NRIC)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-tew0mw-026\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-nyjayn-027\">Passport</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-210u14-028\" data-indent=\"1\"><em>Please ensure the ID is valid (not expired) and that the photo, full name, and ID number are clearly visible.</em></p><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"false\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"mh4d54qn-v97re3-060\"><strong>List of Acceptable ID Documents</strong></p></summary><div data-type=\"details-content\"><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appqBHC8o2cBmTQk1/shrE9BYtdhX7anNwy\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\" class=\"airtable-embed\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\"></iframe></p></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"></h4><ol data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-3wrjpt-018\" start=\"2\" type=\"a\" style=\"--start:1;\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\">Proof of Address</h4><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\">If your government-issued ID does <strong>NOT</strong> contain your residential address, you will be prompted to upload a separate document displaying your address</p><ol data-block-id=\"mh4epvzh-6razm3-145\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eq1rs-smohed-157\"> Any official document that states your residential address (e.g. utility bill, phone bill, tenancy agreement, etc.)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eq1rs-smohed-157\">Document must include your full name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eq1rs-smohed-157\">Document must be a digital download, not scanned or photographed from a physical document</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\"></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\">Proof of Authorization</h4><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-v3mxj9-032\">This document verifies that the <strong>Authorized Representative has the legal right to act on behalf of the company</strong> for the purpose of onboarding with Xendit.</p></li></ol><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-4ch8o6-033\" data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-tkqlkm-034\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-g0vz79-035\">If the representative is <strong>declared in the legal documents submitted, and based on your country’s legal requirements, they are recognized as the authorized representative, you do not need to upload a separate document.</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-nin9db-036\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-kqidne-037\">If the representative is <strong>NOT</strong> <strong>legally able to represent the company by their role/title, you MUST upload a formal document proving their authority</strong>, such as:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-qljw6t-038\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-zy85rs-039\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-50oosf-040\"><strong>Board Resolution Granting Authority</strong>: A resolution signed by at least two (2) Directors and one (1) Company Secretary. This document must clearly state that you are authorized to represent and verify the company's details.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-cfu5px-041\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-dcenuq-042\"><strong>Letter of Authorization (LOA)</strong>: A formal letter on company letterhead signed by a legally authorized person (e.g. Director) explicitly granting you the authority to complete the Xendit application.</p></li></ul></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-ww6fdi-044\">Liveness Verification test</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-n850sk-046\">As a final step to verify that the Authorized Representative is a real person and that the submitted documents belong to them, you will be required to complete an active Liveness Verification test.</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4e3xll-kicd48-025\"><img data-block-id=\"mh4e4zvr-03cl4q-150\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(153).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-i61gj6-047\">This process involves using your device's camera to capture a series of movements or actions:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-5u20nl-048\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-scua9o-049\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-7m0ki6-050\"><strong>Be prepared:</strong> Ensure you are in a well-lit area and that your face is clearly visible.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-l3i59r-051\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-r2u2tj-052\"><strong>Follow the prompts:</strong> The system will guide you through simple actions (e.g., moving your head) to confirm you are present and alive.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-wefixz-053\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-jkmi3t-054\"><strong>Camera Access:</strong> Make sure Xendit has permission to access your camera and that no other applications are currently using it.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-wefixz-053\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-jkmi3t-054\"><strong>Microphone Access (in some cases): </strong>Make sure Xendit has permission to access your microphone and that no other applications are currently using it.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-whxi88-055\">Note: You must pass the liveness verification for the onboarding process to be complete. If you encounter issues (like \"Camera not accessible\"), you may need to check your browser or operating system settings to grant access.</p>","SeoTitle":"Authorized representative requirements","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Authorized Representative Requirements","Slug":"authorized-representative-requirements","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Authorized Representative Requirements","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Authorized Representative Requirements","Slug":"authorized-representative-requirements","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Authorized Representative Requirements","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Requisitos del representante autorizado","Slug":"authorized-representative-requirements","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvx-uj3eyy-006\">Para verificar su negocio, requerimos información sobre el <strong>Representante Autorizado </strong>que está completando este proceso de onboarding en nombre de su entidad legal. </p><p data-block-id=\"mh4dygkf-2ncdex-145\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4dyh4o-bxr4wb-147\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;\">¿Quién es el Representante Autorizado?</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4dyh4o-v7gjoe-149\">El <strong>Representante Autorizado es la persona que está llenando la solicitud de onboarding de Xendit en nombre de su empresa</strong>. Esta persona será nuestro punto de contacto principal para el proceso de solicitud y debe estar legalmente facultada para firmar documentos y asumir compromisos para el negocio.</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4e66fd-nhpbzk-026\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvx-87mkyo-007\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"><img data-block-id=\"mh4e2x1h-obfc66-024\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image-1761282186132.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"812\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"yes\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:812px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvy-fcqal0-012\">Información requerida</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lvy-6gom1k-014\">El Representante Autorizado debe completar los siguientes campos en el flujo de onboarding:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"904\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:904px;width:904px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:452px;\"><col style=\"width:452px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e7clw-37iie0-028\">Categoría</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e7i6o-9lj40a-031\">Detalles Requeridos</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e7rza-m08tf2-053\">Datos Personales</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eboky-xeus5u-131\">Nombre, Apellido, Género, Fecha de Nacimiento</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e8w3z-0xxam1-122\">Información de Contacto</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4ec21d-ui47kg-134\">Dirección de correo electrónico, Número de teléfono</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e94tu-h4ruod-124\">Dirección Residencial</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4echnz-6j8cmf-136\">Dirección Residencial Completa (País, Línea de Dirección 1, Ciudad, Estado/Provincia, Código Postal)</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e9bal-8r6s7k-126\">Nacionalidad</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eefs2-64bc1z-141\">País de Ciudadanía/Nacionalidad</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4e9g7x-e720rc-128\">Cargo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"452\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4efctl-hwmyq7-143\">El cargo oficial del representante dentro de la empresa.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><hr class=\"hr-divider1\" style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(128, 128, 128);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(128, 128, 128) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;line-height:1.15 !important;\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw3-hmnuio-016\">Documentos de verificación requeridos</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw3-vc88co-018\">Para confirmar la identidad y autoridad del representante, se deben presentar los siguientes documentos:</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4dlvlv-5aj77e-010\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"></p><ol data-block-id=\"mh4dmldp-coropw-012\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4dmldp-vrr880-013\"><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4dlvvy-gj8egg-011\">Prueba de Identidad</h4><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-1e6pxg-022\">Debe cargar una copia clara de una identificación válida emitida por el gobierno. Se le pedirá que seleccione el tipo de identificación que está presentando:</p></li></ol><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-j9kw2l-023\" data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-bibosk-024\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-mz9hqc-025\">Identificación Nacional (p. ej., INE)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-tew0mw-026\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-nyjayn-027\">Pasaporte</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-210u14-028\" data-indent=\"1\"><em>Por favor, asegúrese de que la identificación sea válida (no expirada) y que la foto, el nombre completo y el número de identificación sean claramente visibles.</em></p><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"false\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"mh4d54qn-v97re3-060\"><strong>Lista de Documentos de Identificación Aceptables</strong></p></summary><div data-type=\"details-content\"><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appqBHC8o2cBmTQk1/shrE9BYtdhX7anNwy\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\"  class=\"airtable-embed\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\"></iframe></p></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\" style=\"line-height:1.15;animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background:none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);inset:auto;clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;\"></h4><ol data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-3wrjpt-018\" start=\"2\" type=\"a\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\">Comprobante de Domicilio</h4><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\">Si su identificación emitida por el gobierno <strong>NO</strong> contiene su dirección residencial, se le pedirá que cargue un documento por separado que muestre su dirección</p><ol data-block-id=\"mh4epvzh-6razm3-145\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eq1rs-smohed-157\"> Cualquier documento oficial que indique su dirección residencial (p. ej., factura de servicios públicos, factura de teléfono, contrato de arrendamiento, etc.)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eq1rs-smohed-157\">El documento debe incluir su nombre completo</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4eq1rs-smohed-157\">El documento debe ser una descarga digital, no escaneado ni fotografiado de un documento físico</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\"></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4dnx43-6a2j6e-019\"><h4 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-238vbt-030\">Prueba de Autorización</h4><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-v3mxj9-032\">Este documento verifica que el <strong>Representante Autorizado tiene el derecho legal de actuar en nombre de la empresa</strong> para el propósito de la incorporación a Xendit.</p></li></ol><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-4ch8o6-033\" data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-tkqlkm-034\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-g0vz79-035\">Si el representante está <strong>declarado en los documentos legales presentados y, según los requisitos legales de su país, es reconocido como el representante autorizado, no necesita cargar un documento por separado.</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-nin9db-036\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-kqidne-037\">Si el representante <strong>NO</strong> está <strong>legalmente capacitado para representar a la empresa por su cargo/título, DEBE cargar un documento formal que demuestre su autoridad</strong>, como:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-qljw6t-038\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-zy85rs-039\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-50oosf-040\"><strong>Resolución del Consejo que Otorga Autoridad</strong>: Una resolución firmada por al menos dos (2) Directores y un (1) Secretario de la Compañía. Este documento debe indicar claramente que usted está autorizado para representar y verificar los detalles de la empresa.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-cfu5px-041\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-dcenuq-042\"><strong>Carta de Autorización (LOA)</strong>: Una carta formal en papel membretado de la empresa, firmada por una persona legalmente autorizada (p. ej., un Director), que le otorga explícitamente la autoridad para completar la solicitud de Xendit.</p></li></ul></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw4-ww6fdi-044\">Prueba de Verificación de Vida</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-n850sk-046\">Como paso final para verificar que el Representante Autorizado es una persona real y que los documentos presentados le pertenecen, se le pedirá que complete una prueba activa de Verificación de Vida.</p><p data-block-id=\"mh4e3xll-kicd48-025\"><img data-block-id=\"mh4e4zvr-03cl4q-150\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(153).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-i61gj6-047\">Este proceso implica el uso de la cámara de su dispositivo para capturar una serie de movimientos o acciones:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-5u20nl-048\"><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-scua9o-049\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-7m0ki6-050\"><strong>Esté preparado:</strong> Asegúrese de estar en un área bien iluminada y que su rostro sea claramente visible.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-l3i59r-051\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data--block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-r2u2tj-052\"><strong>Siga las instrucciones:</strong> El sistema lo guiará a través de acciones simples (p. ej., mover la cabeza) para confirmar que está presente y es una persona real.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-wefixz-053\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-jkmi3t-054\"><strong>Acceso a la cámara:</strong> Asegúrese de que Xendit tenga permiso para acceder a su cámara y que ninguna otra aplicación la esté utilizando.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-wefixz-053\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-jkmi3t-054\"><strong>Acceso al micrófono (en algunos casos): </strong>Asegúrese de que Xendit tenga permiso para acceder a su micrófono y que ninguna otra aplicación lo esté utilizando.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mh4d0lw5-whxi88-055\">Nota: Debe pasar la verificación de vida para que el proceso de onboarding se complete. Si encuentra problemas (como \"Cámara no accesible\"), es posible que deba revisar la configuración de su navegador o sistema operativo para otorgar el acceso.</p>","SeoTitle":"Requisitos del representante autorizado","Description":null}]